{"id": "1eba18c9524c4f0ce239ebbb3e98c16889e7fd9c0240783bdce607522aed1a49", "item_id": "7bb1135909:0", "text": "PxrTileManifold will compute st mapping coordinates to create textured tiles over a 2D surface. This manifold is able to introduce randomness to hide repeating patterns, if need be."}
{"id": "805bc9cb552b4e61015c9aa4813207845ead5938fa8879abcfef493ee6decd67", "item_id": "7bb1135909:1", "text": "In the example above, the wooden floor was created by plugging a PxrTileManifold in a"}
{"id": "9ae2347670686481700f49f3a1c4674060684d86bd495b4dfc1617426f7f64a8", "item_id": "7bb1135909:20", "text": "PxrMultiTexture"}
{"id": "c61531d2e56409e1d424b7e0289412356378cc24302457f86552761d480d6783", "item_id": "7bb1135909:3", "text": "to assemble multiple textures into a tiled wooden floor."}
{"id": "b29adba5a76af3c0307151ee9127e802a8279b74b72733c80d0e4bd1f555fea0", "item_id": "7bb1135909:5", "text": "used 10 different wood plank textures that were randomly picked and graded."}
{"id": "b090cf634d159b4036894d646fcf91dae1288893a0fc1bfb8ae531e842652df6", "item_id": "7bb1135909:6", "text": "See below for the shading graph and the source textures."}
{"id": "87765cc4cbdb81824e32e28fe02289d34733229c7091972da8eb0188a9cd6845", "item_id": "7bb1135909:7", "text": "PxrTileManifold can only be used with"}
{"id": "a450afa45220562659272138e3ac03e6fa8df812be7f181efe89303764f177cb", "item_id": "7bb1135909:11", "text": "Number of Textures"}
{"id": "f202723341a65cfeaf18efa7a165e07f93be6c8f3d032090d40d141cb8189644", "item_id": "7bb1135909:12", "text": "The number of textures you want to use. You should have at least one texture and"}
{"id": "72a29249f19a5550fe225b7eb5410540632ee6ff59b7ae514f0a1d178f7c2631", "item_id": "7bb1135909:14", "text": "supports up to 10 textures."}
{"id": "833047ff4d5793ea0ce27106c6a5ebf808db97e83bb26a0a213d307479e2db12", "item_id": "7bb1135909:15", "text": "This value will be passed to connected"}
{"id": "b5d75275e0fab9bbbbb0fb2d8060ee88d60a668df962b48ef60f426ddf8a8872", "item_id": "7bb1135909:17", "text": "nodes, so you may control the number of variations from a single location."}
{"id": "6be86eadbf0ce307cb75488915f5662e9d60a93075880359ed7a3c85d46b8bfe", "item_id": "7bb1135909:18", "text": "Texture Order"}
{"id": "c291fba66043e293a8293122f8b36c7409825f5f05999659e3524ce72f5869d2", "item_id": "7bb1135909:19", "text": "The textures can be assigned in different ways. They can either be enumerated in the order in which they appear in the"}
{"id": "1bf60d619cd5ccce21b680a7b6cf10a0e3195f5482050b0d743dca6be5a97433", "item_id": "7bb1135909:21", "text": "node or be randomly selected."}
{"id": "8e37953d23daca5ff01b8282c33f4e0a2152f1d1885f94c06418617e3ee1d24e", "item_id": "7bb1135909:39", "text": "Value"}
{"id": "5e23ec6a300dc60a79641769017e16e9bf042cbd8fd0a54586a048ab9da972ff", "item_id": "7bb1135909:23", "text": "Mode"}
{"id": "007877479e2173b20d7a60df177ccce8cb2db376f63cf42f9b2d5c221444a376", "item_id": "7bb1135909:24", "text": "Ordered"}
{"id": "67bc484430fe87babe3c35d2ba4827d029f1c7e415a92de44885a9c88536661f", "item_id": "7bb1135909:25", "text": "Random"}
{"id": "c83f11fb4b1badc2851df2bd5cf6dce8a74764490495305591d77db99320f800", "item_id": "7bb1135909:26", "text": "Pattern Settings"}
{"id": "8429165800a7282491a8af5f7ba6613fa72b88faaa3649c4c20cd67ae0017436", "item_id": "7bb1135909:27", "text": "Grid offset"}
{"id": "cab9142b3ec3722afa306110d4910a3e0f1a67a815150fbfc03406bb35c30011", "item_id": "7bb1135909:28", "text": "The textures are organised in a regular grid arrangement with an optional offset. This is useful for brick or wooden floor patterns, for examples."}
{"id": "acada119c137d5c69f172f684b639b1ec17ec9ae9334a3647c1a797d9db76fe8", "item_id": "7bb1135909:29", "text": "Grout Width"}
{"id": "10d00098e5e549fa7d345d3d84c8a91de29ac3c3e8aeb2cd998643a801c3b79b", "item_id": "7bb1135909:30", "text": "The grout is the space between the tiles. When set to 0.0, there is no space between the tiles. The maximum value is 1.0, where the tiles disappear."}
{"id": "252cd5e36b582bb594679997b45233b72f5f3df9a851948d17b225d92bba66ae", "item_id": "7bb1135909:31", "text": "Tile Bevel Width"}
{"id": "2af2a306ee9b15bb5d1309b6cfe84d5c56fbae2f7a6b20a228bfe6d547c5e49a", "item_id": "7bb1135909:32", "text": "This parameter will control the width of the transition from the grout to the tile. This can be used to shape the tiles' displacement amplitude."}
{"id": "f55501d6b1a8b32899e09c0721cf50ebe9ba58274e670ad6a6866cb09e47283a", "item_id": "7bb1135909:33", "text": "Swap Tile ST"}
{"id": "19c53f254925a85561dc383947bcb305ae4ec533ccda98087f551af9a55bd649", "item_id": "7bb1135909:34", "text": "Sometime your textures are not oriented correctly and this control will rotate the tile's local st coordinates by swapping s and t."}
{"id": "1f7483c8a10473d3d369e45e15775a286449f3934eec0c370dbf46e0af413366", "item_id": "7bb1135909:35", "text": "Randomize"}
{"id": "d069e8002b0aa476fc2f6ade310f102a89e72cacc08da6e2b2de859a2e9003d9", "item_id": "7bb1135909:36", "text": "Random Source"}
{"id": "7902fd8e623687b81862df95bf5eb85c1cffe9955789fca742de909a39027083", "item_id": "7bb1135909:37", "text": "For each object to get a different variation, you need to select something unique about them to create a unique seed. You have a choice between the object's id and the object's name."}
{"id": "75ec6906b7ed311e60cba05ae1b6a37c79e32173651a1da2491ee0a43e668fc9", "item_id": "7bb1135909:38", "text": "These attributes are created by the software outputting the RIB and depending on your application (Maya, Katana, etc...), one may work better than the other."}
{"id": "0e570ca6fabe24f94e52c1833f3ffd25567022beb826fa16891f3322051bc221", "item_id": "7bb1135909:40", "text": "Source"}
{"id": "fcb4dd842c61858a8dffb91fc365fce2203f19260b8bcfc4c100a983404973eb", "item_id": "7bb1135909:41", "text": "Depends on"}
{"id": "480de93d13fc774797a1b9d9f04e6378c51c7535fb9797961b51c370e7fc5e57", "item_id": "7bb1135909:42", "text": "Object id"}
{"id": "6b355b68c0ec1c3147ed3cc10acc5777264b8d250cf1f969723bc454a1f2f348", "item_id": "7bb1135909:43", "text": "Attribute \"identifier\" \"float id\""}
{"id": "df9bc7bfc7f33b956dbcc76e3096e17dea346efd4f55f5bda33e76d8be875225", "item_id": "7bb1135909:44", "text": "Object Name"}
{"id": "09d1fc54d19ab4259a0b703e9b8c106f709644fb7f4997f0708c9d646622f7ac", "item_id": "7bb1135909:45", "text": "Attribute \"identifier\" \"string name\""}
{"id": "287d18467622df3f977b8a1dc22e12ad35e5024f271fe96c1f4f6b326c6f6bda", "item_id": "7bb1135909:46", "text": "Extra Seed"}
{"id": "6694e959b273734dae618458fac3847595448d7a170521cca4f6ae54b7b753d4", "item_id": "7bb1135909:47", "text": "If you want one of these patterns to compute a different variation, set the randomExtraSeed to a non-zero value. This parameter will only influence the randomization parameters (randomOrientation, randomFlipS, etc)."}
{"id": "ad8f9fee37994bbd50a0cd4afb7ffacd27e5c8ef503d05bf9024473ea120a3d4", "item_id": "7bb1135909:48", "text": "Random Orientation"}
{"id": "439fabe8903efd768b1929295f7c2b5421fa2c5f8f0d0005b09bd7056cf31d18", "item_id": "7bb1135909:49", "text": "Randomize the orientation of the textures by randomly swapping s and t."}
{"id": "4718158121fb2cec5b1839a50dcdb4a273746401d9f0d35b9c6b32d0004f08be", "item_id": "7bb1135909:50", "text": "Random S Flip"}
{"id": "922be1a8e7ac417a199232be39d0d1bad185236ebe9189cb3cf142b71bac992f", "item_id": "7bb1135909:51", "text": "Randomly flip the direction of s."}
{"id": "220e9aea516a7a45fe5c2bb5dff9c7f95c7c8760f5fdbcdf4d0a434325bc8d68", "item_id": "7bb1135909:52", "text": "Random T Flip"}
{"id": "7ec1d0856d0f48c41b84c3a113028ad1366fc7c18b11328287f3f9fda1525406", "item_id": "7bb1135909:53", "text": "Randomly flip the direction of t."}
{"id": "2e87cd67afab8c0c97a04f427e0c6f14f71bd63f2a0072ff13110a8089d03021", "item_id": "7bb1135909:54", "text": "Random S Offset"}
{"id": "90b01a33a2e13848986468bd91a98ecaa404e749b002bc9bbd628c41189c21d4", "item_id": "7bb1135909:55", "text": "Randomly offset s. You should probably avoid this if your textures are not tiling seamlessly."}
{"id": "15582bfeee8edfbccf7bf07bd8363ec008dd07b76496f1bc06d873a8904b5142", "item_id": "7bb1135909:56", "text": "Random T Offset"}
{"id": "76c98e52b2170acb1f963d068f51531027d47fc05329dae80a6be53bc1c69de0", "item_id": "7bb1135909:57", "text": "Randomly offset t. You should probably avoid this if your textures are not tiling seamlessly."}
{"id": "7598dc637d7766288323328a9bc69dbce01f1c82d603dcb9bb238087659bdcc7", "item_id": "7bb1135909:58", "text": "Manifold 2D"}
{"id": "1968034b13f84d0c3e441fcc8b5f3ec7b75fcabdbcecb68177445498557d3e33", "item_id": "7bb1135909:59", "text": "Angle"}
{"id": "751f11467c33d49fdaa1dadc5dda35332eb09fa17831247452e5d20fd3f147c2", "item_id": "7bb1135909:60", "text": "Global rotation angle around the origin of the st domain."}
{"id": "dfce4fe1a66ce3ba0da2f5bc8c567f5a562d9d83b7fa89c000352b073ea4a014", "item_id": "7bb1135909:61", "text": "Global Scale"}
{"id": "5c42bba8bbf93884288fba8d4fc0527679bb4249adcabfe24503e5f47309c491", "item_id": "7bb1135909:62", "text": "Scale the st domain while preserving the aspect ratio defined by scaleS and scaleT."}
{"id": "de02ff6a41bb301f28ff4320ea109951b8f00c4bdbd06a50b8b1d6b7d6546538", "item_id": "7bb1135909:63", "text": "Scale S"}
{"id": "2564778edb13c55c5704dbda23c55c7740547bbefc04866f22568c1597bfd1a3", "item_id": "7bb1135909:64", "text": "Frequency of the feature in S."}
{"id": "74ed367dd43611959a619b470a288d25878f785a729581a3ec0df16a3ae880b4", "item_id": "7bb1135909:65", "text": "Scale T"}
{"id": "a2289dde977d612c255d04d2aa22bcab76f76152340c97017f8d21ad50e15003", "item_id": "7bb1135909:66", "text": "Frequency of the feature in T"}
{"id": "79182e90c534c862c9a1371a047fc3b73fd5f5b657802cfcfd78324f778ab585", "item_id": "7bb1135909:67", "text": "Offset S"}
{"id": "60c39a0a6caf7f89dc14a9413b5bae5265d3b00ee10715de89f806e4b2766c34", "item_id": "7bb1135909:68", "text": "Offset from origin in S."}
{"id": "f25c3396d562c4c180fe177b4acefab8f7fbb413aa193189fa71a156ca5bfd7d", "item_id": "7bb1135909:69", "text": "Offset T"}
{"id": "90fef1d5351323e45eecc5d8d1e27b64ee864613ba47b6fa465719d47a512a20", "item_id": "7bb1135909:70", "text": "Offset from origin in T."}
{"id": "7b4e3156de47599b1c25274775d4aa507a2ae5e23a74591b475e50c192b5d2e5", "item_id": "7bb1135909:71", "text": "invert T"}
{"id": "bdcc8e9a52362a6c87e62a9a6ef6199d1ed930751caa77128f7e56872e4a1ea0", "item_id": "7bb1135909:72", "text": "Invert the direction of T."}
{"id": "9f67c9d4c723ae1283959412cd003591d6f42d81a2c0d7e0595fa6b3ec8942c4", "item_id": "7bb1135909:73", "text": "PrimVar S/ST"}
{"id": "d31d863c6937c847e07b1befac39f36d6075b41d3439f4513cbf6ce9ba5b0aa4", "item_id": "7bb1135909:74", "text": "Name of custom 1D S or 2D ST primvar."}
{"id": "ff6decb98de33f019292f6f4ff9f2e2afa4aac8f87a3fffd33365b3fcd630822", "item_id": "7bb1135909:75", "text": "PrimVar T"}
{"id": "b6110b12756c83957293a5ef6710b1ee8d3460b15b726d4690e4db2c8d932fc8", "item_id": "7bb1135909:76", "text": "Name of custom 1D T primvar."}
{"id": "4d862f1addeaf474213e01f3d949e06372fd1b7dbe8a83fda1b83c1ce23c717d", "item_id": "7bb1135909:79", "text": "This is a regular 2D manifold output."}
{"id": "62e08e2bb387da80cfcb1864abcdba7367159ab023b20921fd2b4129bc754537", "item_id": "7bb1135909:80", "text": "Result S"}
{"id": "588d58cce73e5600fb8381146412c61a5e8abd1a1d30c5141d4e3fdf22341e34", "item_id": "7bb1135909:81", "text": "Outputs only the computed S value."}
{"id": "e3e52d81aff197a20f102ab7c8a5ec11cf31b848eff88ee34f2d8cf8cfb627a4", "item_id": "7bb1135909:82", "text": "Result T"}
{"id": "e5bc4530dd4e9fcf545d7c2f74b5eefe74c741054d2ad9283c595f78054877c3", "item_id": "7bb1135909:83", "text": "Outputs only the computed T value."}
{"id": "fca4a04970fd211db466ec40195f09b57dd7fb3a2462ba550cb026ea46829367", "item_id": "7bb1135909:84", "text": "Result Multi"}
{"id": "84013b18343db358284e689cebd3e57bfe6e72dcb3f8b98f2dd7000264a6765c", "item_id": "7bb1135909:85", "text": "Outputs a multiManilfold, compatible with PxrMultiTexture."}
{"id": "72617dcd02956c09e4e72af6082f5cbc10016044296801512d4929a9cdd63426", "item_id": "7bb1135909:86", "text": "Result Mask"}
{"id": "8bcd8259d6194388316c4beae8a95125a4c25a16a906f4b942e8929913933473", "item_id": "7bb1135909:87", "text": "This is a color output containing the following data:"}
{"id": "ce4683e7013a18cdf3d224bfcb4e9594ea8f559e946a837c633defe7d3c32172", "item_id": "7bb1135909:88", "text": "Channel"}
{"id": "60caa24883d4893688daa661aa29ab8a534ccb1c09d3dfe2c37c0d3d53031ff5", "item_id": "7bb1135909:90", "text": "1.0 if this is an odd tile in S, 0.0 otherwise"}
{"id": "bc3b15be97524528df337aa252afa67d2d54816868ebba6e43f6ce5ccc558196", "item_id": "7bb1135909:91", "text": "1.0 if this is an odd tile in T, 0.0 otherwise"}
{"id": "092f3a529057a389823655940475f625814ff1caab335ab9075c6531af825a69", "item_id": "7bb1135909:92", "text": "Grout mask"}
